column5: Rustic but clean and cozy. Newly remodeled inside. Direct path to Lake Whitney. Close to public boat ramp ( parking is available for boats, if you have one, bring it! ) Close to Bosque Resort and water park, fishing, hunting, water sports, state parks, bird watching, photography, antique shopping, walking trails, 35 minutes to Waco, 15 minutes to Hillsboro.
